  "pageTitle": "AI高价值塑料回收废物分类机",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page product-page-ai\">\n      <section class=\"section split-section\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">AI 废物光学分拣机</p>\n          <h1>AI高价值塑料回收废物分类机</h1>\n          <p class=\"hero-copy\">WEI LAN AI光学废弃物分拣机通过材料和颜色识别PET瓶、HDPE瓶、PP及其他混合塑料。模块化配置 支持 自动废物分拣系统、MRF设备升级以及紧凑型智能回收设施，需要稳定的连续分拣。</p>\n          <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n            <a class=\"text-link is-hud\" href=\"/contact\">请求提案</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"../assets/images/recyclable-plastic-sorting-line.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <img src=\"/assets/images/recyclable-plastic-sorting-line.png\" alt=\"AI可回收塑料废弃物的光学分类线\">\n        </picture>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section\" id=\"models\" aria-labelledby=\"models-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">模型参数</p>\n          <h2 id=\"models-title\">GL01V系列</h2>\n          <p>共享AI分拣平台上的三种配置。按吞吐量和物料类别选择。</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"spec-card-grid spec-card-grid-ai\">\n          <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-1\">\n            <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n              <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-01</span>\n              <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V1-5</p>\n                <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">迷你版</p>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <i></i><i></i>\n              </span>\n            </header>\n            <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:35%\">\n                <dt>容量</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.6&ndash;0.8<small>t/h</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:55%\">\n                <dt>动力</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">30<small>千瓦</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:38%\">\n                <dt>覆盖范围</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">24<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安装占地 ·8 × 3 m版面 ·3 m 净空高度</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:50%\">\n                <dt>分选范围</dt>\n                <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">5<small>物料类型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分选范围：透明PET·彩色PET·HDPE ·PP ·混合塑料\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · color PET · HDPE · PP · mixed plastics\">PET ·HDPE ·PP ·混合</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-2\">\n            <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n              <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-02</span>\n              <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V2-9</p>\n                <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">标准</p>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <i></i><i></i>\n              </span>\n            </header>\n            <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:58%\">\n                <dt>容量</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.8&ndash;1.2<small>t/h</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:78%\">\n                <dt>动力</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">45<small>千瓦</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:62%\">\n                <dt>覆盖范围</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">36<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安装占地 ·12 × 3 m版面 ·6 m 净空高度</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:90%\">\n                <dt>分选范围</dt>\n                <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">9<small>物料类型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分选范围：透明PET·绿色PET ·蓝色PET ·混色PET·白色HDPE·彩色HDPE·PP ·混合塑料·拒绝\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · mixed plastics · reject\">PET颜色·HDPE ·PP ·混合·拒绝</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-3\">\n            <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n              <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-03</span>\n              <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V3-10</p>\n                <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">而且</p>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <i></i><i></i>\n              </span>\n            </header>\n            <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:95%\">\n                <dt>容量</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">1.5&ndash;2<small>t/h</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\">\n                <dt>动力</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">53<small>千瓦</small></span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\">\n                <dt>覆盖范围</dt>\n                <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">51<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安装占地 ·17 × 3 m版面 ·6 m 净空高度</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                <dt>分选范围</dt>\n                <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">10<small>物料类型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分选范围：透明PET·绿色PET ·蓝色PET ·混色PET·白色HDPE·彩色HDPE·PP ·PE ·混合塑料·拒绝\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · PE · mixed plastics · reject\">PET颜色·HDPE ·PP ·PE ·混合·拒绝</span></dd>\n                <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section sorting-performance-section\" aria-labelledby=\"sorting-performance-title\">\n        <div class=\"sorting-performance-head\">\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">分拣性能</p>\n            <h2 id=\"sorting-performance-title\">AI分选性能，围绕可测量的回收性构建</h2>\n            <p>GL01V将AI识别、光学传感、气流喷射喷射、循环输送和数字报告结合在一个紧凑的塑料回收和MRF升级分拣中心中。</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"sorting-feed-panel\" aria-labelledby=\"sorting-feed-title\">\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"sorting-panel-kicker\">供料材料</p>\n            <h3 id=\"sorting-feed-title\">配置为瓶装和刚性塑料回收</h3>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"sorting-feed-grid\" aria-label=\"公认的塑料流示例\">\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-clear\"><b>PET</b><small>清场</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-green\"><b>PET</b><small>绿色</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-blue\"><b>PET</b><small>蓝色</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-pet-mixed\"><b>PET</b><small>混色</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-hdpe\"><b>HDPE</b><small>白色</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-hdpe-colored\"><b>HDPE</b><small>有色</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-pp\"><b>PP</b><small>刚性</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-pe\"><b>PE</b><small>目标</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-mixed\"><b>混合</b><small>塑料</small></span>\n            <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-reject\"><b>拒绝</b><small>溪流</small></span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"sorting-data-band\" aria-label=\"GL01V分选性能指标\">\n          <div class=\"sorting-data-copy\">\n            <p class=\"sorting-panel-kicker\">紧凑分拣中心</p>\n            <h3>高回收数据，采用可改装的占地面积</h3>\n            <p>Mini、Standard 和 Plus 布局从紧凑的 试点 产线 扩展到更大规模的 MRF 试点 产线，同时保持相同的 AI/HUD 操作逻辑。</p>\n            <div class=\"sorting-mode-switch\" aria-label=\"布局状态\">\n              <span>工作</span>\n              <span>交通</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"sorting-data-grid\">\n            <article>\n              <span>类别</span>\n              <strong>10<small>类型 MAX</small></strong>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span>容量</span>\n              <strong>2<small>t/h max</small></strong>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span>动力</span>\n              <strong>30<small>千瓦最小功率</small></strong>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span>覆盖范围</span>\n              <strong>24<small>m<sup>2</sup> 明</small></strong>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span>布局</span>\n              <strong>滑架<small>已装甲</small></strong>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span>快速改装</span>\n              <strong>17<small>days fastest</small></strong>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"sorting-smart-panel\">\n          <div class=\"sorting-feature-intro\">\n            <p class=\"sorting-panel-kicker\">智能机器</p>\n            <h3>操作员准备控制栈</h3>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"sorting-feature-grid\" aria-label=\"分拣中心优势\">\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-ai\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>AI荣誉</h3>\n              <p>更高的回收价值：AI识别PET、HDPE、PP、PE、混合塑料，并以较少依赖人工判断的废弃流。</p>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-air\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>气流-jet 分选</h3>\n              <p>稳定输出纯度：快速的气流喷射能准确去除目标，同时线路保持连续通量。</p>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-sensors\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>传感器控制</h3>\n              <p>降低纯度风险：实时传感器信号在输出质量下降前暴露识别、压力、时序和物料流漂移。</p>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-rate\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>96-98%的分选率</h3>\n              <p>96-98%分拣性能：宣传册中列出的高精度 支持 高纯度回收目标，用于塑料回收和MRF升级。</p>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-robot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>机器人准备布局</h3>\n              <p>降低劳动力压力：机器人准备布局为减少手工拣选留有空间，以适应物料体积增长。</p>\n            </article>\n            <article>\n              <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-cockpit\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <h3>数字驾驶舱</h3>\n              <p>更快的决策：实时状态、警报、运行时间、分选统计、碳排放指示器和视频流都汇聚在同一视图中。</p>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section dark-section product-process-section\" aria-labelledby=\"plastic-process-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">流程概述</p>\n          <h2 id=\"plastic-process-title\">从进食到数字报告的塑料回收流程</h2>\n          <p>光学分拣系统围绕清晰的物料路径组织，买家可以评估送料、预选、物料分拣、颜色分拣和操作数据在生产线中的定位。</p>\n        </div>\n        <ol class=\"process-timeline\" aria-label=\"塑料回收工艺\">\n          <li class=\"process-timeline-step\">\n            <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-01</span>\n            <div class=\"process-timeline-card\">\n              <div class=\"process-timeline-body\">\n                <h3>给料</h3>\n                <p>以受控速率将消费后的瓶子或混合的可回收塑料放入分拣线。</p>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"给料过程视频\">\n                <div class=\"process-timeline-video\">\n                  <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\">\n                    <source src=\"/assets/video/AI上料.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                    你的浏览器不会支持视频元素。\n                  </video>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"process-timeline-step\">\n            <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-02</span>\n            <div class=\"process-timeline-card\">\n              <div class=\"process-timeline-body\">\n                <h3>预分选</h3>\n                <p>在下游分拣前，将金属集装箱与由其他材料制成的瓶子区分开来。</p>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"预分选过程视频\">\n                <div class=\"process-timeline-video\">\n                  <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\">\n                    <source src=\"/assets/video/AI预分.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                    你的浏览器不会支持视频元素。\n                  </video>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"process-timeline-step\">\n            <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-03</span>\n            <div class=\"process-timeline-card\">\n              <div class=\"process-timeline-body\">\n                <h3>材料分类</h3>\n                <p>按目标树脂类别区分塑料，以提高回收价值并减少人工依赖。</p>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"材料分拣过程视频\">\n                <div class=\"process-timeline-video\">\n                  <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\">\n                    <source src=\"/assets/video/AI分拣.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                    你的浏览器不会支持视频元素。\n                  </video>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"process-timeline-step\">\n            <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-04</span>\n            <div class=\"process-timeline-card\">\n              <div class=\"process-timeline-body\">\n                <h3>颜色分类</h3>\n                <p>按颜色PET瓶子及其他目标材料分组，项目价值依赖于更清洁的比例。</p>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"颜色分类过程视频\">\n                <div class=\"process-timeline-video\">\n                  <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\">\n                    <source src=\"/assets/video/AI出料.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                    你的浏览器不会支持视频元素。\n                  </video>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"process-timeline-step\">\n            <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-05</span>\n            <div class=\"process-timeline-card\">\n              <div class=\"process-timeline-body\">\n                <h3>数字报道</h3>\n                <p>跟踪吞吐量、类别、设备状态、警报和碳排放相关操作指标。</p>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"数字报道视频占位符\">\n                <div class=\"process-timeline-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"视频即将发布\">\n                  <span class=\"process-timeline-video-tag\">CAM-05</span>\n                  <span class=\"process-timeline-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n                  <span class=\"process-timeline-video-label\">视频即将发布</span>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </li>\n        </ol>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section product-compare-section\" aria-labelledby=\"compare-title\" hidden>\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">产品比较</p>\n          <h2 id=\"compare-title\">GL01V与行业基线</h2>\n          <p>WEI LAN AI光学分拣机如何与对比比较，典型的分选线，决定了驱动总拥有成本的指标。</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"product-compare-layout\">\n          <figure class=\"product-compare-explode\" aria-label=\"GL01V爆炸视角\">\n            <div class=\"product-compare-explode-frame\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"爆炸视图图即将发布\">\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-tag\">爆炸 ·GL01V2-9</span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:18%;--pin-y:32%\" data-label=\"01\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:38%;--pin-y:58%\" data-label=\"02\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:58%;--pin-y:26%\" data-label=\"03\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:74%;--pin-y:64%\" data-label=\"04\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:88%;--pin-y:40%\" data-label=\"05\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-label\">爆炸视角即将上线</span>\n            </div>\n            <figcaption>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-meta\">5 模块化滑橇·标准模具</span>\n            </figcaption>\n          </figure>\n\n          <div class=\"product-compare-panel\">\n            <header class=\"product-compare-panel-head\">\n              <span class=\"product-compare-legend\">\n                <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-self\"></span>WEI LAN GL01V\n              </span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-legend\">\n                <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-base\"></span>行业基线\n              </span>\n            </header>\n\n            <ul class=\"product-compare-list\" role=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-01</span>\n                  <h3>部分与整体的比例</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">单位成本占比</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:38%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">WEI LAN</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">38%</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:62%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基线</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">62%</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">较低的备件比例意味着折旧更慢，使用寿命 维护。</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-02</span>\n                  <h3>覆盖范围</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">标准层为m²</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:55%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">WEI LAN</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">36 m²</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基线</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">65 m²</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">滑架式布局适合紧凑的 MRF 房间和路边回收站。</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-03</span>\n                  <h3>容量</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">T/H，标准等级</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:88%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">WEI LAN</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">0.8 – 1.2</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:62%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基线</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">0.6 – 0.9</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">优化的馈源+AI识别提升了相同足迹级别的吞吐量。</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-04</span>\n                  <h3>功耗</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">千瓦，标准级别</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:60%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">WEI LAN</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">45 kW</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基线</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">75 kW</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">按额定吞吐量计算，每吨分拣功率约降低40%。</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-05</span>\n                  <h3>运输与组装</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">服役天数</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:35%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">WEI LAN</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">3 – 5 天</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:90%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基线</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">10 – 14 天</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">预接线滑架模块以标准集装箱出厂;现场工作仅限螺栓和钢索。</p>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section ai-faq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"ai-faq-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">常见问题</p>\n          <h2 id=\"ai-faq-title\">AI买家在RFQ前会问的光学分类问题</h2>\n          <p>这些答案帮助回收操作员、EPC团队和设备采购者评估AI光学分拣机是否适合其物料流和项目阶段。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ai-faq-panel\">\n          <article class=\"ai-faq-item\">\n            <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-01</span>AI光学分拣机能分离哪些材料？</h3>\n            <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">该系统设计用于可回收塑料流，如PET瓶、HDPE瓶、PP、混合硬塑料以及颜色基PET分组，包括透明瓶、绿色瓶、蓝色瓶和混合色瓶。</p>\n            <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n              <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需输入</span>\n              <span>资料照片或视频</span>\n              <span>目标输出类别</span>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"ai-faq-item\">\n            <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-02</span>什么因素影响AI垃圾分拣机的价格？</h3>\n            <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">价格取决于吞吐量、物料类别、分拣模块数量、送料和打包范围、数字控制需求、安装 支持，以及项目是否需要与现有MRF设备集成。</p>\n            <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n              <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需输入</span>\n              <span>目标吞吐量</span>\n              <span>分选模块范围</span>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"ai-faq-item\">\n            <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-03</span>一条光学分拣线能处理多大容量？</h3>\n            <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">GL01V车型涵盖0.6-2 t/h。最终尺寸应根据材料成分、污染程度、期望纯度、可用 封面积及 每日 的操作时间进行检查。</p>\n            <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n              <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需输入</span>\n              <span>每日 运营时间</span>\n              <span>可用 占地面积</span>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"ai-faq-item\">\n            <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-04</span>该系统能否添加到现有的回收设施中？</h3>\n            <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">当买方提供当前工艺布局、进料状况、输送机高度、控制需求和目标输出时，可以评估整合性。滑架安装结构 支持 实用改装讨论。</p>\n            <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n              <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需输入</span>\n              <span>现有线路布局</span>\n              <span>输送机高度与控制点</span>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section ai-rfq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"ai-rfq-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">RFQ准备</p>\n          <h2 id=\"ai-rfq-title\">准备数据包以AI分拣器尺寸</h2>\n          <p>在报价前发送这些输入，以便工程团队确认分拣范围、设备型号、布局可行性和集成风险。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ai-rfq-checklist\">\n          <article>\n            <span>01</span>\n            <h3>资料照片或视频</h3>\n            <p>显示皮带上的进料流、捆管状况、污染程度和正常操作条件下的颜色混合。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span>02</span>\n            <h3>目标吞吐量</h3>\n            <p>确认每小时容量、每日的运营时间、高峰负荷，以及线路是否需要一个或多个分拣模块。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span>03</span>\n            <h3>输出类别</h3>\n            <p>列出所需的分PET，如透明、PET绿色、PET蓝色、HDPE、PP、混合塑料或拒接流。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span>04</span>\n            <h3>现有线路布局</h3>\n            <p>提供输送机高度、可用可覆盖面积、上游送料方式、下游打包机位置及控制接口需求。</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"rfq-action-strip\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">请求工程审查</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/resources\">准备文件包</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
